Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:12.54,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4\fs28}在追忆的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:16.67,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4\fs28}静静地摇曳
